  <channel>
    <title>Women and Girls contributor: Smriti Sharma</title>
    <description>Smriti Sharma is a research fellow at UNU-WIDER in Helsinki, Finland. Her research interests are in development economics, behavioral economics and labor economics. She has worked on caste and gender-based discrimination in India and Bangladesh, analyzing caste-based crimes, caste gaps in self-employment, the effect of caste on behavioral preferences and personality traits, and gender wage gaps. She holds a PhD in economics from the Delhi School of Economics.
 
</description>
